item.description: DALLAS , Nov. 17, 2021 /PRNewswire/ -- Kimberly-Clark today announced that it was named one of the 2021 Top 75 Companies for Executive Women by Seramount (formerly Working Mother Media ) for the fifth consecutive year. This honor recognizes U.S. corporations that champion women's advancement,
